"The |saveAsSVG| :sup:`Export as SVG` icon saves the print layout as an "
":file:`SVG` (Scalable Vector Graphic)."
msgstr ""
"|saveAsSVG| :sup:`Export as SVG` 아이콘을 클릭하면 인쇄 조판을 :file:`SVG` (Scalable "
"Vector Graphic) 파일로 저장할 수 있습니다."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_composer/create_output.rst:642
msgid "saveAsSVG"
msgstr "saveAsSVG"

